data.description: Charming cottage a few homes from the lake looking for its next owners.  Come take a look at this 3 bedroom, 1 bath home with roomy kitchen with appliances, laundry room with washer and dryer, resilient vinyl flooring, fenced in back yard,  parking off alley with garden shed and room for a garage, walking distance to the lake for all the activities that are offered, minutes to town, schools, etc.  Make your appointment today for your own private tour.
